headline.print_headline: Europe; Greece: Premier Wins Confidence Vote
headline.main: Greece: Premier Alex Tsipras Wins Confidence Vote

snippet: As expected, all 155 lawmakers in the governing coalition in the 300-member Parliament backed Mr. Tsipras.
abstract: Greece's governing coalition and Prime Min Alexis Tsipras win confidence vote, strengthening efforts to meet bailout terms and revive country's economy.
lead_paragraph: As expected, all 155 lawmakers in the governing coalition in the 300-member Parliament backed Mr. Tsipras.
